Module java.base
Package jdk.internal.classfile.attribute

Interface ModuleAttribute

All Superinterfaces:
Attribute<ModuleAttribute>, ClassElement, ClassfileElement, WritableElement<ModuleAttribute>
public sealed interface ModuleAttribute extends Attribute<ModuleAttribute>, ClassElement
Models the Module attribute 4.7.25, which can appear on classes that represent module descriptors. Delivered as a ClassElement when traversing the elements of a ClassModel.
